---
title: Chicken Breast and French-Inspired Lentil Salad with Herby Goat Cheese and Walnuts
description: Satisfying and sophisticated, this salad makes a superb supper! Marinated lentils provide a hearty salad base with pan-seared chicken and creamy, tangy goat cheese is rolled in fresh herbs for a luxurious topping!
